ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:08:43.730 --> 00:08:47.150
INTERPRETER: To fight
anxiety and tension.

00:08:47.150 --> 00:08:50.380
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:08:54.772 --> 00:08:56.980
INTERPRETER: It's better to
forget what you're doing.

00:08:56.980 --> 00:08:59.630
Just think, this is normal,
this part of our lives.

