life that spurred that desire?

00:09:22.010 --> 00:09:24.730
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:09:24.730 --> 00:09:27.220
INTERPRETER: It wasn't my fault.

00:09:27.220 --> 00:09:30.020
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:09:34.402 --> 00:09:36.110
INTERPRETER: It's
always been others that

00:09:36.110 --> 00:09:38.380
