00:09:38.380 --> 00:09:41.680
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:09:43.674 --> 00:09:45.340
INTERPRETER: Since I
was a little child,

00:09:45.340 --> 00:09:48.270
