00:10:09.620 --> 00:10:13.650
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:10:14.419 --> 00:10:16.710
INTERPRETER: So I started
singing at birthday parties--

00:10:16.710 --> 00:10:18.970
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:10:18.970 --> 00:10:21.730
INTERPRETER: The church,
