00:10:40.380 --> 00:10:45.220
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:10:49.195 --> 00:10:50.820
INTERPRETER: So step
by step, I started

00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:53.600
