this might be my future.

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:57.730
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:10:59.952 --> 00:11:01.410
INTERPRETER: I
mean, people ask me,

00:11:01.410 --> 00:11:03.460
what do you need to
