00:11:42.340 --> 00:11:42.840
Law Firm.

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:46.442
INTERPRETER: [SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:11:46.442 --> 00:11:47.650
DANIEL ALEGRE: What happened?

00:11:47.650 --> 00:11:48.941
INTERPRETER: [SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:11:48.941 --> 00:11:52.930
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:11:57.786 --> 00:12:00.900
INTERPRETER: In my family,
several of my relatives

00:12:00.900 --> 00:12:01.930
