00:12:29.690 --> 00:12:33.890
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:12:34.514 --> 00:12:35.930
INTERPRETER: And
it made me become

00:12:35.930 --> 00:12:37.910
