ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:03.530
INTERPRETER: I got sick.

00:17:03.530 --> 00:17:08.710
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:08.710 --> 00:17:12.440
INTERPRETER: And my I sang
with high temperature.

00:17:12.440 --> 00:17:16.190
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:16.190 --> 00:17:20.579
INTERPRETER: But I had an
angel on my side and I made it.

00:17:20.579 --> 00:17:23.000
DANIEL ALEGRE: And
after more than 20 years

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:26.700
of performing live, do you still
get nervous going up on stage?

00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:28.950
And if you do, how
do you handle that?

00:17:28.950 --> 00:17:30.670
INTERPRETER: [SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:31.470 --> 00:17:36.260
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:39.816 --> 00:17:41.440
INTERPRETER: You're
always nervous when

00:17:41.440 --> 00:17:43.770
you sing in front of a
