00:17:43.770 --> 00:17:45.580
an intimate thing.

00:17:45.580 --> 00:17:47.389
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:47.389 --> 00:17:49.680
INTERPRETER: It's something
that comes from the inside.

00:17:49.680 --> 00:17:55.370
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:17:58.774 --> 00:18:00.440
INTERPRETER: Singing
in front of someone

00:18:00.440 --> 00:18:04.100
who came to hear you
