in front of them.

00:18:06.970 --> 00:18:12.400
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:18:18.780 --> 00:18:21.200
INTERPRETER: So there's always
this sense of [ITALIAN],

00:18:21.200 --> 00:18:23.290
you never know how
you feel when you are

00:18:23.290 --> 00:18:26.120
in front of these audiences.

00:18:26.120 --> 00:18:29.130
DANIEL ALEGRE: And
what does the song

00:18:29.130 --> 00:18:32.890
"Time to Say Goodbye" mean
