00:19:53.830 --> 00:19:56.525
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:19:56.525 --> 00:19:58.980
INTERPRETER: You'll
hardly believe me--

00:19:58.980 --> 00:20:04.800
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:06.150 --> 00:20:09.090
INTERPRETER: Here we have
a few-- sorry-- witnesses

00:20:09.090 --> 00:20:11.505
