00:20:11.505 --> 00:20:13.500
that can witness it for you.

00:20:13.500 --> 00:20:18.360
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:21.030 --> 00:20:23.030
INTERPRETER: I don't care
what happens around me

00:20:23.030 --> 00:20:25.020
from the business point of view.

00:20:25.020 --> 00:20:28.129
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:28.129 --> 00:20:29.920
INTERPRETER: Sometimes,
I come to a concert

00:20:29.920 --> 00:20:31.560
