00:20:31.560 --> 00:20:36.455
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:38.039 --> 00:20:39.830
INTERPRETER: Many people
ask me, how many--

00:20:39.830 --> 00:20:44.300
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:44.300 --> 00:20:46.760
INTERPRETER: I don't know
