00:20:53.770 --> 00:20:55.512
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:55.512 --> 00:20:57.406
INTERPRETER: [SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:20:57.406 --> 00:20:59.267
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

