00:21:37.640 --> 00:21:41.490
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:21:41.490 --> 00:21:44.670
INTERPRETER: Everyone needs
to do well what he does.

00:21:44.670 --> 00:21:50.816
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:21:54.454 --> 00:21:56.870
INTERPRETER: There's people
who take care of the business.

