00:24:57.980 --> 00:25:00.110
ANDREA BOCELLI:
It's so magic, no?

00:25:00.110 --> 00:25:05.890
To listen to our voice in
a small box is incredible.

00:25:05.890 --> 00:25:08.880
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:25:14.027 --> 00:25:15.610
INTERPRETER: And
since then, I started

00:25:15.610 --> 00:25:22.380
collecting a countless number
of technological pieces.

00:25:22.380 --> 00:25:26.045
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:25:27.830 --> 00:25:30.920
INTERPRETER: I visited every
single shop here in America

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:34.950
