00:26:07.220 --> 00:26:09.526
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:09.526 --> 00:26:11.650
INTERPRETER: But I have
trust, I have faith in man.

00:26:11.650 --> 00:26:16.360
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:16.557 --> 00:26:18.640
INTERPRETER: And I'm sure
that man eventually will

00:26:18.640 --> 00:26:20.220
make good use of technology.

00:26:20.220 --> 00:26:26.350
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:39.540 --> 00:26:41.270
INTERPRETER: Technology
made huge steps.

00:26:41.270 --> 00:26:44.540
Just imagining a small
box, you can have thousands

00:26:44.540 --> 00:26:49.420
