00:26:49.420 --> 00:26:54.360
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:54.360 --> 00:26:58.665
INTERPRETER: All this required
a lot of money in the past,

00:26:58.665 --> 00:26:59.230
