00:26:59.230 --> 00:27:02.720
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:04.520
INTERPRETER: Now it's
all in your pocket.

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:09.260
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:27:14.274 --> 00:27:16.190
INTERPRETER: This is an
