00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:25.970
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:27:25.970 --> 00:27:28.380
INTERPRETER: And this means
equality, in one word.

00:27:28.380 --> 00:27:32.880
ANDREA BOCELLI:
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:27:38.890 --> 00:27:40.780
INTERPRETER: Not
a forced equality,

00:27:40.780 --> 00:27:44.020
forced by blood and
